The '''Caixa Económica de Cabo Verde''' is a [[Cape Verde]]an [[commercial bank]]. Its headquarters are at [[Avenida Cidade de Lisboa]] in [[Praia]].<ref>[http://www.caixa.cv/Conteudos/Artigos/detalhe.aspx?idc=1346&idsc=2439&idl=2 Contacts], Caixa Económica de Cabo Verde</ref> It was established in 1928 as ''Caixa Económica Postal''. In 1985 it was transformed into an autonomous financial institution named Caixa Económica de Cabo Verde. In 1993 it became a [[limited liability company]].<ref>[http://www.caixa.cv/Conteudos/Artigos/detalhe.aspx?idc=1346&idsc=1347&idl=2 History], Caixa Económica de Cabo Verde</ref>
