ador]] |1992<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=SYjisekAKn8C&pg=PA74&lpg=PA74&dq=BVES+el+salvador&source=bl&ots=1g9ql7tq4y&sig=-ic_g3zxF2uAdlm7CiBo6V7nsMY&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CF4Q6AEwDGoVChMIjNaAiYfoxgIVzCoeCh06AgCC#v=onepage&q=BVES%20el%20salvador&f=false Investment Policy Review: El Salvador] by United Nations Conference on Trade and Development</ref> |align="right"| |[https://www.bolsadevalores.com.sv/ BVES] |- |{{flagicon|Guatemala}} '''[[Guatemala]]''' | | |align="right"| | |- |[[Bolsa Nacional de Valores]] |[[Guatemala City]] |1987 |align="right"| |[http://www.bvnsa.com.gt/ |- |{{flagicon|Honduras}} '''[[Honduras]]''' | | |align="right"| | |- |[[Bolsa Centroamericana de Valores]] |[[Tegucigalpa]] | |align="right"| |[http://www.bcv.hn/ BCV] |- |[[Bolsa Honduras de Valores]] | | |align="right"| |[https://web.archive.org/web/20040902074948/http://www.bhv.hn/ BHV] |- |{{flagicon|Nicaragua}} '''[[Nicaragua]]''' | | |align="right"| | |- |[[Bolsa de Valores de Nicaragua]] |[[Managua]] |1990 |align="right"| |[http://www.bolsanic.com BVDN] |- |{{flagicon|Panama}} '''[[Panama]]''' | | |align="right"| | |- |[[Bolsa de Valores de Panamá]] |[[Panama City]] |1989 |align="right"| |[http://www.panabolsa.com/ BVP] |- |<big>'''''[[South America]]'''''</big> | | | | |- |{{flagicon|Argentina}} '''[[Argentina]]''' | | | | |- |[[Buenos Aires Stock Exchange]] |[[Buenos Aires]] |1854 |align="right"| |[http://www.bcba.sba.com.ar/ BCBA] |- |[[Mercado Abierto Electrónico]] |[[Buenos Aires]] |1988 |align="right"| |[http://www.mae.com.ar/ MAE] |- |[[Rosario Stock Exchange]] |[[Rosario]] |1884 |align="right"| |[http://www.bcr.com.ar/ BCR] |- |- |- |{{flagicon|Bolivia}} '''[[Bolivia]]''' | | | | |- |[[Bolsa Boliviana de Valores]] |[[La Paz, Bolivia|La Paz]] |1990 |align="right"| |[http://www.bolsa-valores-bolivia.com BVB] |- |{{flagicon|Brazil}} '''[[Brazil]]''' | | | | |- |[[BM&F Bovespa]] |[[São Paulo]] |1890 |align="right"| |[http://www.bovespa.com.br Bovespa] |- |[[Rio de Janeiro Stock 