'''Lohusa Şerbeti''' or '''Lohusa Sherbet''' is a traditional [[Drink|beverage]] in Turkey, made with [[water]], [[sugar]], [[cinnamon]], [[clove]]s, and red food colour.<ref name="btcb-2010" /><ref name="asct-2011" />  It is usually given to women after [[childbirth]], but it is also now shared with visitors and friends as well.<ref name="asct-2011" />

