{{Infobox language |name=Majera |states=[[Chad]], [[Cameroon]] |region= |speakers=500 |date=2004 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Afro-Asiatic |fam2=[[Chadic languages|Chadic]] |fam3=[[Biu–Mandara languages|Biu–Mandara]] |fam4=East–Central |fam5=[[Mida'a languages|Mida’a]] |iso3=xmj |glotto=maje1243 |glottorefname=Majera }} '''Majera''' (Mazᵉra) is a minor [[Afro-Asiatic language]] of Chad and Cameroon.
