'''Massulo''' is a town and [[Communes of Angola|commune]] of [[Angola]], located in the province of [[Luanda Province|Luanda]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://censo.ine.gov.ao/xportal/xmain?xpid=censo2014&xpgid=provincias&provincias-generic-detail_qry=BOUI=10505453&actualmenu=10505453|title=Luanda|last=|first=|date=|website=Official Portal of the 2014 INE Angola Census|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=30 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.google.co.uk/maps/place/Mussulo/@-8.9636714,13.0168242,13z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x1a52276439c8b6d1:0xc543d6f21f8fc657!8m2!3d-8.963758!4d13.051758|title=Massulo|last=|first=|date=|website=google maps|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=30 May 2018}}</ref>
