[[San Marino]] is a small sovereign state located within the territory of [[Italy]]. It has a musical heritage which includes the 17th-century composer [[Francesco Maria Marini di Pesaro]] and the 20th-century composer Cesare Franchini Tassini (1925–2010).

Since 1894, a wordless composition by [[Federico Consolo]] has been the [[national anthem]] of San Marino. The piece is based on a 10th-century [[choir|choral]] composition.<ref>[http://david.national-anthems.net/sm.htm National Anthems Reference Page]</ref> The previous anthem was by Aur. Muccioli and U. Balsimelli, and is similar to the Italian national anthem.<ref>[http://david.national-anthems.net/sm-94.htm National Anthems Reference Page]</ref>

The modern [[military of San Marino|military forces of San Marino]] parade through the streets in full uniform several times a day, accompanied by the sounds of a military [[brass band]].<ref>[http://berclo.net/page99/99en-san-marino.html Travelogues]</ref>

There is a small metal scene with Necrofilia<ref>[https://www.facebook.com/zazzinecrofilia Necrofilia Facebook]</ref> and Nothing Inside Eyes<ref>[https://www.facebook.com/pg/nothinginsideeyes/about/?ref=page_internal Nothing Inside Eyes Facebook]</ref> the latter being formed from another band called Alchimia 2012.<ref>[http://www.metal-archives.com/bands/Alchimia_2012/3540260032 Metal Archives]</ref>

