'''Quadirabad Cantonment''' is a cantonment located in [[Natore District|Natore]], [[Rajshahi division]], [[Bangladesh]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Qadirabad Cantonment Public School, Natore|url=http://www.dmlc.gov.bd/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=67&Itemid=146|website=dmlc.gov.bd|accessdate=4 April 2017|language=en-gb}}</ref>
==History== The Cantonment was named after Lt Col [[Abdul Qadir (officer)|Abdul Qadir]] who died in the [[Bangladesh Liberation war]]. He was buried in a mass grave in an unknown site. His son Nadeem Qadir discovered the grave in Comilla and he was reburied in the cantonment on September 2011.<ref>{{cite web|title=War hero laid to rest, finally|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/news-detail-203672|website=The Daily Star|accessdate=4 April 2017|language=en|date=23 September 2011}}</ref>
==Units== *5th Engineering Corps<ref>{{cite web|last1=Ahmed|first1=Hafez|title=PM praises support of army engineers in dev activities|url=http://print.thefinancialexpress-bd.com/old/more.php?news_id=123193&date=2012-03-12|website=print.thefinancialexpress-bd.com}}</ref> *Engineer Centre and School of Military Engineering (ECSME) *Station Headquarters, Qadirabad Cantonment *ECSME Training Battalion
==Institutions== *[[Qadirabad Cantonment Public School]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Girls do better than boys in Rajshahi board|url=http://archive.dhakatribune.com/education/2014/dec/31/girls-do-better-boys-rajshahi-board|website=archive.dhakatribune.com|publisher=Dhaka Tribune|accessdate=4 April 2017|language=en}}</ref> *[[Bangladesh Army University of Engineering & Technology]]<ref>{{cite web|title=BAUET: Bangladesh Army University of Engineering & Technology|url=http://www.bauet.ac.bd/|website=bauet.ac.bd|accessdate=4 April 2017|language=en}}</ref> *[[Qadirabad Cantonment Sapper College]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Qadirabad Cantonment Sapper College, Natore|url=http://institute.alormela.org/bangladesh/rajshahi/nator/national-university-college/748-qadirabad-cantonment-sapper-college-natore|website=institute.alormela.org|accessdate=4 April 2017|language=en-gb}}</ref> *Combined Military Hospital<ref>{{cite web|title=Army man killed in Natore road crash|url=http://www.banglanews24.com/national/article/57987/Army-man-killed-in-Natore-road-crash|website=banglanews24.com|accessdate=4 April 2017|language=en}}</ref>
